import React from 'react'

const ComA = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <select v>
            <option value="1"> 1 </option>
            <option value="25"> 25 </option>
            <option value="3"> 3 </option>
            <option value="4"> 4 </option>
            <option value="5"> 5 </option>
        </select>
    </>
  )
}

export default ComA
